column5: Wow that's amazing.  Glad he made it, what a scary situation that would be.
Wow, that is crazy. Always wear your lifevest, and keep communication devices handy.
Quite a story KF  Anyone who has ever been lost in the backwoods likely also knows how many bottles of beer are on that wall  And ya can sing as loud and off key as ya like-----sans critics
Bin there done that.   Thanks Rob.
